column6: Spider-Girl's hunt for the new Doctor Octopus is sidetracked by Claw, the Cat, a high-tech villain who's faster, stronger, and more agile than our girl! Plus: an unexpected cliffhanger!
column8: | inker:Sal Buscema | writer:Tom DeFalco | penciller (cover):Ron Frenz | penciller:Patrick Olliffe | colorist:Angelo Tsang
